ikipedia:Infundibulum_of_uterine_tube].\" xsd:string {source=\"Wikipedia:Infundibulum_of_uterine_tube\"}\nproperty_value: taxon_notes \"In mammals, the uterine tube infundibulum is part of the fallopian tube. In birds, where there is no fallopian tube, the uterine tube infundibulum is part of the oviduct.\" xsd:string {xref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2825-0621\"}\n\n","exit":0,"description":"Shows UBERON 0003984 stanza","truncated":false},"title":"Shows UBERON 0003984 stanza","time":{"start":1778379047100,"end":1778379047103}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_06a240a0fbe2d5630169ffe926f72881909f9b45b40a5f0f34"}},"id":"prt_e0fa6c065001E4CXcAJ2XMrIrR","sessionID":"ses_1f059cf3fffes9xNkcvd273qv7","messageID":"msg_e0fa6aae2001qVN4t7y8rxPRaW"}}
